                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="112r" to="112r" scheme="folios"/>: miniature; Pentecost.</p>
                                    <p> Following immediately after the last prayer is an addition of 7 lines which appears to pertain to the next item, Hours of the Trinity; it begins, <quote>Pater noster Incipit officium de trinitate Ave maria</quote>.</p>
                                </note>
                            </msItem>
